name: latto latto the battle
description:
This is a game about latto latto which is currently being played in Indonesia and the genre of this game is rhythm

Tells the story of gouns who is good at playing latto latto, he is also challenged by enemies such as aliens and also other people from several countries.

Ini adalah game tentang latto latto yang saat ini sedang dimainkan di Indonesia dan genre game ini adalah ritme

Berkisah tentang gouns yang jago bermain latto latto dia pun ditantang oleh musuh nya seperti alien dan juga orang lain yang dari beberapa negara gitu
